<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>About Us — <%- site.businessName %></title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:wght@300;400;500;600&family=Jost:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/about-page.css">
</head>
<body>

  <%- include('partials/header') %>

  <!-- PAGE HERO -->
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="page-hero-inner">
      <span class="section-label">Our Story</span>
      <h1>About <%- site.businessName %></h1>
      <p>We're a team of employment lawyers dedicated to helping people understand and enforce their workplace rights.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- MISSION & VALUES -->
  <section class="about-section about-mission">
    <div class="about-inner">
      <div class="about-content">
        <span class="section-label">Who we are</span>
        <h2>Our mission</h2>
        <p><%- site.businessName %> exists to help people navigate employment disputes and understand their rights at work. We believe that every employee deserves to be treated fairly, paid correctly, and work in an environment free from harassment and discrimination.</p>
        <p>We take the complexity out of employment law so you can focus on moving forward with your life and your career. Whether you're facing dismissal, a dispute with your employer, or simply need advice about your rights, we're here to help.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="about-values">
        <div class="value-card">
          <h3>Integrity</h3>
          <p>We give you honest advice about the strength of your case and what's realistically achievable.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-card">
          <h3>Accessibility</h3>
          <p>We offer flexible fee arrangements and free initial consultations so you can access legal advice when you need it most.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-card">
          <h3>Excellence</h3>
          <p>We're committed to the highest standards of legal work and client service on every matter.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-card">
          <h3>Empathy</h3>
          <p>We understand that employment disputes are stressful. We listen, we care, and we support you throughout the process.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- WHY CHOOSE US -->
  <section class="about-section about-why">
    <div class="about-inner">
      <span class="section-label">What sets us apart</span>
      <h2>Why choose <%- site.businessName %>?</h2>
      <div class="why-grid">
        <div class="why-item">
          <div class="why-icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2zm0 18c-4.42 0-8-3.58-8-8s3.58-8 8-8 8 3.58 8 8-3.58 8-8 8zm3.5-9c.83 0 1.5-.67 1.5-1.5S16.33 8 15.5 8 14 8.67 14 9.5s.67 1.5 1.5 1.5zm-7 0c.83 0 1.5-.67 1.5-1.5S9.33 8 8.5 8 7 8.67 7 9.5 7.67 11 8.5 11zm3.5 6.5c2.33 0 4.31-1.46 5.11-3.5H6.89c.8 2.04 2.78 3.5 5.11 3.5z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Specialist expertise</h3>
          <p>We focus exclusively on employment law, so we know this area inside and out. We're not generalists — we're specialists in helping people with workplace issues.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="why-item">
          <div class="why-icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2zm-2 15l-5-5 1.41-1.41L10 14.17l7.59-7.59L19 8l-9 9z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Track record of success</h3>
          <p>We've helped dozens of people recover unpaid wages, secure compensation for unfair treatment, and hold employers accountable. We're proud of what our clients have achieved with our help.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="why-item">
          <div class="why-icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M17 10.5V7c0-.55-.45-1-1-1H4c-.55 0-1 .45-1 1v10c0 .55.45 1 1 1h12c.55 0 1-.45 1-1v-3.5l4 4v-11l-4 4z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Clear communication</h3>
          <p>We explain things in plain English, not legal jargon. You'll understand what's happening, why we're doing it, and what it means for your case.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="why-item">
          <div class="why-icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 1C5.9 1 1 5.9 1 12s4.9 11 11 11 11-4.9 11-11S18.1 1 12 1zm0 20c-4.97 0-9-4.03-9-9s4.03-9 9-9 9 4.03 9 9-4.03 9-9 9zm3.5-9c.83 0 1.5-.67 1.5-1.5S16.33 9 15.5 9 14 9.67 14 10.5s.67 1.5 1.5 1.5zm-7 0c.83 0 1.5-.67 1.5-1.5S9.33 9 8.5 9 7 9.67 7 10.5 7.67 12 8.5 12zm3.5 6.5c2.33 0 4.31-1.46 5.11-3.5H6.89c.8 2.04 2.78 3.5 5.11 3.5z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Responsive & accessible</h3>
          <p>We're available when you need us and we answer your calls and emails promptly. Employment disputes are often stressful and time-sensitive — we get that.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="why-item">
          <div class="why-icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M19 3H5c-1.1 0-2 .9-2 2v14c0 1.1.9 2 2 2h14c1.1 0 2-.9 2-2V5c0-1.1-.9-2-2-2zm0 16H5V5h14v14zm-5.04-6.71l-2.75 3.54-2.16-2.66c-.23-.29-.62-.29-.85 0-.23.29-.23.77 0 1.06l2.58 3.15c.23.29.62.29.85 0l3.16-4.05c.23-.29.23-.77 0-1.06-.23-.29-.62-.29-.85 0z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Flexible fee options</h3>
          <p>We offer hourly, fixed, and no win, no fee arrangements to suit different situations. Your first consultation is always free, so there's no risk in talking to us.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="why-item">
          <div class="why-icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 8c1.1 0 2-.9 2-2s-.9-2-2-2-2 .9-2 2 .9 2 2 2zm0 2c-1.1 0-2 .9-2 2s.9 2 2 2 2-.9 2-2-.9-2-2-2zm0 6c-1.1 0-2 .9-2 2s.9 2 2 2 2-.9 2-2-.9-2-2-2z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Your advocate</h3>
          <p>We're on your side. We fight for your rights and negotiate hard to get you the best possible outcome — whether that's compensation, a fair settlement, or vindication.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- EXPERIENCE -->
  <section class="about-section about-experience">
    <div class="about-inner">
      <div class="experience-content">
        <span class="section-label">Experience & credentials</span>
        <h2>Our team</h2>
        <p>Our team brings together decades of combined experience in employment law. We've worked both for employers and for employees, which gives us a unique perspective on how workplace disputes develop and how to resolve them fairly.</p>
        <p>We're members of the Law Society of New Zealand and bound by strict professional standards. We take our obligation to clients seriously and approach every case with the care and attention it deserves.</p>
        <p>When you work with us, you're getting specialists who know employment law inside and out, combined with people who genuinely care about helping you get the best possible outcome.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="experience-stats">
        <div class="stat">
          <div class="stat-num">20+</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Years of combined experience</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat">
          <div class="stat-num">200+</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Employment disputes resolved</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat">
          <div class="stat-num">$5M+</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Recovered for clients</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat">
          <div class="stat-num">98%</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Client satisfaction rate</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- APPROACH -->
  <section class="about-section about-approach">
    <div class="about-inner">
      <span class="section-label">How we work</span>
      <h2>Our approach</h2>
      <div class="approach-steps">
        <div class="approach-step">
          <div class="approach-step-num">01</div>
          <div class="approach-step-content">
            <h3>Listen</h3>
            <p>We start by listening. We want to understand your situation, what matters to you, and what you're hoping to achieve. We ask questions and we genuinely care about the answers.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="approach-step">
          <div class="approach-step-num">02</div>
          <div class="approach-step-content">
            <h3>Assess</h3>
            <p>We assess the strength of your case honestly. We'll tell you what we think you have, what the risks are, and what's realistically achievable. We don't oversell and we don't mislead.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="approach-step">
          <div class="approach-step-num">03</div>
          <div class="approach-step-content">
            <h3>Advise</h3>
            <p>We advise you on your legal options in plain English. We explain what each option means, what it costs, and what the likely outcomes are so you can make an informed decision.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="approach-step">
          <div class="approach-step-num">04</div>
          <div class="approach-step-content">
            <h3>Act</h3>
            <p>We take action on your behalf. We prepare documents, write letters, negotiate with your employer, and represent you at mediation or in proceedings. We keep you informed at every step.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="approach-step">
          <div class="approach-step-num">05</div>
          <div class="approach-step-content">
            <h3>Resolve</h3>
            <p>We work toward a resolution that's fair and achieves what matters to you. We negotiate hard but reasonably, always mindful of your interests and the best path forward.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="approach-step">
          <div class="approach-step-num">06</div>
          <div class="approach-step-content">
            <h3>Support</h3>
            <p>We support you through the process. We understand that employment disputes can be stressful and we're here to help you navigate them with confidence.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CONTACT CTA -->
  <section class="about-contact">
    <div class="about-contact-inner">
      <span class="section-label">Ready to get started?</span>
      <h2>Let's talk about your situation</h2>
      <p>Your first consultation is free and comes with no obligation. We'll listen to your situation, explain your rights, and tell you what we can do to help.</p>
      <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary">Get in touch</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <%- include('partials/footer') %>

  <script src="/js/main.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
